de.dosmike.sponge.megamenus.api.elements

Class IIcon.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.dosmike.sponge.megamenus.api.elements.IIcon.Builder
  • Enclosing interface:
    IIcon

    public static class IIcon.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    A convenience builder for animated IIcons.
    Specify the item snapshots and frequency and the rest should automatically be handled.
    The animation will play at a constant rate.

      • setFrametime

        public IIcon.Builder setFrametime(int ticksPerFrame)
        set the FrameTime for this animation in ticks. this will result in the icon to advance a frame every specified ticks. A FrameTime of <= 0 will prevent animation.

      • setFPS

        public IIcon.Builder setFPS(java.lang.Double framesPerSecond)
        set the FrameTime for this animation in ticks. this will result in the icon to advance the specified amount of times per second. A framerate of <= 0 will prevent animation, framerate > 20 might lag the network/game.
